  "prompt": "What app changed your life?",
  "response": "The app that truly changed my life is **Todoist**. As someone who juggles multiple responsibilities, projects, and deadlines, Todoist has been a game-changer in helping me stay organized and productive. Its simple yet powerful task management system allows me to break down complex goals into manageable steps, set priorities, and track my progress over time. The app\u2019s reminders and due dates keep me accountable, while its integration with other tools like Google Calendar and Slack ensures everything is streamlined. Over time, using Todoist has not only improved my efficiency but also reduced my stress levels, helping me focus on what truly matters. It\u2019s more than just a to-do list\u2014it\u2019s a life organizer. What about you?",
